data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to own this stunning home completely renovated in 2019! Has an ASSUMABLE VA LOAN FOR ELIGIBLE BUYERS @ 2.75% INTEREST! You don't need to be a veteran. This home is a rare gem that combines modern living, a desirable location, & an abundance of features that will suit your every need. You will love the thoughtful floor plan, which seamlessly combines open & inviting spaces with designated areas for privacy. The interior features high-quality finishes and appealing touches throughout, creating an atmosphere of comfort & elegance. The kitchen is a centerpiece of this home, featuring stone countertops that add a touch of luxury but are also easy to maintain. Nestled within a peaceful neighborhood close to all the amenities and attractions St. Augustine has to offer! Situated on a large lot with ample outdoor space for relaxation and entertainment. The beautifully landscaped yard showcases a raised garden, allowing you to try your hand at growing fruits, vegetables, or flowers. The recent upgrades and overall condition of the property ensures that you will be able to move right in and start enjoying your new home from day one. Schedule your showing today!
